    <prop:relationInstance>get and set its values using</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>once you have obtained a field reference you can get and set its values using the field.get() and field.set()methods, like this:</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="N0dd8b3a448f6408f97bb2f3b28902566">
