    <prop:relationInstance>has a method called</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>the java list interface has a method called retainall() which is capable of retaining all elements from one list which are also present in another list.</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="N509d520746984be8ad4ab1cd3c34e8d9">
