    <prop:sourceText>the java sortedset interface has a method named headset() which returns another sortedset with all elements that are smaller than (ahead of) a given parameter value, according to the sort order used by the sortedset.</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="N2ad43c01622d46a2973d49f9f943280c">
