    <prop:relationInstance>calls</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>then the thread executing the main() method (the main thread) sleeps for 10 seconds, and then calls the dostop() method of the myrunnable instance.</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="Nb90f4351523045979c476e3f70211ae3">
