    <rdf:predicate rdf:resource="http://example.org/java-kg/property/DIFFERENCE"/>
    <rdf:object rdf:resource="http://example.org/java-kg/individual/offer"/>
    <prop:relationInstance>differ in behavior</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>the add() and offer() methods differ in how the behave if the queue is full, so no more elements can be added. the add() method throws an exception in that case, whereas the offer() method just returns false.</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
