    <prop:relationInstance>thrown via</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>as you can see it is now possible to distinguish an exception thrown from method1() via method2() from the same exception thrown from method1() via method3().</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="N7c89e143ff7d4fe59b0dfb88c7d72c5c">
