    <rdf:object rdf:resource="http://example.org/java-kg/individual/setset"/>
    <prop:relationInstance>has a method named</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>the java sortedset interface has a method named setset() which returns another sortedset with all elements that are greater than or equal to (tailing) a given parameter value, according to the sort order used by the sortedset.</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
