  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="Ne712f0826d614cc3af4e47d228d48946">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Statement"/>
    <rdf:subject rdf:resource="http://example.org/java-kg/individual/donotify%28%29"/>
    <rdf:predicate rdf:resource="http://example.org/java-kg/property/PREFERENCE"/>
    <rdf:object rdf:resource="http://example.org/java-kg/individual/notify"/>
    <prop:relationInstance>preference</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>the problem is, that since the donotify() call only calls notify() and not notifyall(), only one thread is awakened even if 4 threads are waiting on the same string instance (the empty string).</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
