    <prop:sourceText>the java printstream class contains the powerful format() and printf() methods (they do exactly the same, but the name "printf" is more familiar to c-programmers).</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="Nc832480a830c4f7bb12cdb36abd3a294">
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Statement"/>
