    <prop:relationInstance>works the same way as</prop:relationInstance>
    <prop:sourceText>the tailset() method works the same way as the headset() method, except it returns all elements that are equal to or higher than the given parameter element.</prop:sourceText>
  </rdf:Description>
  <rdf:Description rdf:nodeID="N8faf913ad61a4c0faa35099e0114c07e">
